text: Wyndham St. John (born 30 May 1959) is a Canadian equestrian. She competed in the individual eventing at the 2000 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1959 births Category:Living people Category:Canadian female equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Canada Category:Equestrians at the 2000 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Vancouver
